relation: Darrow4 - #98 Charred, but not out yet, the rat attempts to throw in the towel. Unfortunately, it's probably not a great idea to do so after having royally pissed off the main characters.
Darrow4 - #99 Preparing to strike, Ness gets words of support from his friends. Their combined power will finally bring an unfortunate end to the rat's failed plot.
Darrow - #05 Okay, the ball finally starts rolling now. Pokey makes his entrance, which I was all too happy about.

Darrow - #50 With great power...comes great backpain. Captain Strong shows his age and the battle comes to an end. Ness, content with his victory, proceeds onto Twoson and the chapter of Onett comes to a close. Also, a cameo by yours truly as the mysterious Check-a-roony guy.
Darrow5 - #00 With a swing of the bat, Ness' physical strength temporarily peaks and reaches its max. The rat is well aware of what a maxed Guts stat can do to him, and it's not going to be pretty.
